<P><small>Each closed bug report is expired from these logs 28 days after
the last message relating to it is received and filed. You can search the
bug report archive through the forms below, but note that it doesn't contain
the oldest closed bug reports (only those after #40000, approximately).
</small></P>

<h3>Find bug reports</h3>

<p><table border="0" width="100%"><tr>
  <td valign="top">
  <form method="get" action="http://cgi.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi">
  <font face="Arial,Helvetica"><b>
  By number:
  <br>
  <input type="text" size="9" name="bug" value="">
  <input type="submit" value="Fetch">
  </b>
  <br>
  <small>Search the archive?
    <input type="radio" name="archive" value="yes">yes
    <input type="radio" name="archive" value="no" checked>no
  </small>
  </font>
  </form>
  </td>

  <td valign="top">
  <form method="get" action="http://cgi.debian.org/cgi-bin/pkgreport.cgi">
  <font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="+0"><b>
  By package:
  <br>
  <input type="text" size="20" name="pkg" value="">
  <input type="submit" value="Fetch">
  </b>
  <br>
  <small>Search the archive?
    <input type="radio" name="archive" value="yes">yes
    <input type="radio" name="archive" value="no" checked>no
  </small>
  </font>
  </form>
  </td>

  <td valign="top">
  <form method="get" action="http://cgi.debian.org/cgi-bin/aj.pkgreport.cgi">
  <font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="+0"><b>
  By maintainer e-mail:
  <br>
  <input type="text" size="30" name="maint" value="">
  <input type="submit" value="Fetch">
  </b>
  <br>
  <small>Search the archive?
    <input type="radio" name="archive" value="yes">yes
    <input type="radio" name="archive" value="no" checked>no
  </small>
  </font>
  </form>
  </td>
</tr></table>

<p>The above queries can also be made by visiting URLs of the following
forms, respectively:
<ul>
  <li><tt>http://bugs.debian.org/number</tt>
  <li><tt>http://bugs.debian.org/package</tt>
  <li><tt>http://bugs.debian.org/maintainer@email.address</tt>
</ul>

<p><A href="http://cgi.debian.org/cgi-bin/pkgarch.cgi">List of packages</A>.

